name: ORU Missions Manteam Calendar 2013
description:
Help send eight men from ORU to Tanzania, Africa this summer. 

This year's edition features special guests ORU President Dr. Mark Rutland, Dean of Spiritual Formation Dean Boyd, and ORU Missions Director Bobby Parks! Be sure to purchase one while you can! 

This funny and slick calendar will be sure to brighten your wall and your day. It can also be a conversation starter about ORU Missions!

*All proceeds go to supporting the missions team fundraising.
*shipping is $5 plus $1 extra per calendar
